#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:1
msgid "Prescriptions and medications"
msgstr "Prescriptions et médicaments"

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:4
msgid ""
"Manage medication in Resthome — catalogue, prescriptions, administrations, "
"lots and stock, allergies and interactions."
msgstr ""
"Gérer la médication dans Resthome — catalogue, prescriptions, "
"administrations, lots et stock, allergies et interactions."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:7
msgid ""
"Resthome manages a resident's **medication** end to end: from prescription "
"to administration, including stock and safety checks (allergies, "
"interactions)."
msgstr ""
"Resthome gère la **médication** d'un résident de bout en bout : de la "
"prescription à l'administration, en passant par le stock et les contrôles de"
" sécurité (allergies, interactions)."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:10
msgid "The medication catalogue"
msgstr "Le catalogue de médicaments"

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:12
msgid ""
"Available medications are grouped in a **catalogue** (linked to the Belgian "
"**SAM** database). It lists the name, the form and the dosage. It is the "
"source of prescriptions."
msgstr ""
"Les médicaments disponibles sont regroupés dans un **catalogue** (relié à la"
" base belge **SAM**). Vous y retrouvez le nom, la forme, le dosage. C'est la"
" source des prescriptions."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:16
msgid "Prescribing"
msgstr "Prescrire"

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:18
msgid ""
"From the resident's record (Care application), create a **prescription**."
msgstr ""
"Depuis la fiche du résident (application Soins), créez une **prescription**."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:19
msgid "Choose the **medication**, the **dosage** and the **period**."
msgstr "Choisissez le **médicament**, la **posologie** et la **période**."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:20
msgid "**Save.**"
msgstr "**Enregistrez.**"

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:22
msgid "A prescription follows its life cycle with clear actions:"
msgstr "Une prescription suit son cycle de vie avec des actions claires :"

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:24
msgid "**Suspend** — temporarily interrupt (e.g. before an examination)."
msgstr "**Suspendre** — interrompre temporairement (ex. avant un examen)."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:25
msgid "**Resume** — restart a suspended prescription."
msgstr "**Reprendre** — relancer une prescription suspendue."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:26
msgid "**End** — close at the end of the treatment."
msgstr "**Terminer** — clôturer à la fin du traitement."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:27
msgid "**Cancel** — remove a prescription entered by mistake."
msgstr "**Annuler** — supprimer une prescription saisie par erreur."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:29
msgid "Safety: allergies and interactions"
msgstr "Sécurité : allergies et interactions"

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:32
msgid ""
"Resthome knows the resident's **allergies** and the known **drug "
"interactions**. It warns you if a prescription poses a risk — a safeguard "
"before administration."
msgstr ""
"Resthome connaît les **allergies** du résident et les **interactions "
"médicamenteuses** connues. Il vous alerte si une prescription pose un risque"
" — un garde-fou avant l'administration."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:36
msgid "Administering"
msgstr "Administrer"

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:38
msgid ""
"**Administrations** stem from prescriptions: the caregiver records what was "
"given, when and by whom. Traceability is complete."
msgstr ""
"Les **administrations** découlent des prescriptions : le soignant enregistre"
" ce qui a été donné, quand, et par qui. La traçabilité est complète."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:41
msgid "Lots and stock"
msgstr "Lots et stock"

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:43
msgid ""
"The **medication lots** and the **stock withdrawals** let you track the "
"available quantities and consumption, with lot numbers for traceability."
msgstr ""
"Les **lots de médicaments** et les **sorties de stock** permettent de suivre"
" les quantités disponibles et la consommation, avec les numéros de lot pour "
"la traçabilité."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:46
msgid "Useful configuration"
msgstr "Configuration utile"

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:48
msgid "**Pathologies (ICD-10)** — the resident's history and diagnoses."
msgstr "**Pathologies (CIM-10)** — antécédents et diagnostics du résident."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:49
msgid "**Allergens** — known allergies."
msgstr "**Allergènes** — allergies connues."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:50
msgid "**Drug interactions** — vigilance rules."
msgstr "**Interactions médicamenteuses** — règles de vigilance."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:51
msgid "**SAM database** — reference catalogue of Belgian medications."
msgstr "**Base SAM** — référentiel des médicaments belges."

#: ../../content/soins/prescriptions.md:53
msgid "Going further"
msgstr "Pour aller plus loin"

